snippet.title: Magical Monster - New POKÉMON Gameplay (Android/IOS)
snippet.description:
Magical Monster - New POKÉMON Gameplay (Android/IOS)

Trainers, put the pieces of the monster together to complete the task.

Unlock Instances
Unlock as many instances as possible to get experience; play mysterious levels to get more powerful equips

Recruit Pets
Participate in events with diamonds, recruit advanced pets to attack boss quickly

Team Collaboration
Pets are from different camps. Combination of teams could bring special effects.

Guild War
Go to battle with guild members and challenge stronger enemies to get rich rewards.

►► Total Size: 775MB

► Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hw.magic.monster&hl=vi&rdid=com.hw.magic.monster
